snippet.title: art of rally - Game Pass Trailer
snippet.description:
See what all the reviewers have been saying in this brand new trailer for art of rally! 

💥arriving summer 2021 for Xbox One, Xbox Series X, Game Pass, Win10 and xCloud! 💥

art of rally is also available now on PC!
Steam: http://www.bit.ly/steamaor
GOG: http://www.bit.ly/gogaor
Epic: http://www.bit.ly/epicaor

Website: http://artofrally.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/kcVbHR9
Twitter: https://twitter.com/funselektor
Instagram: https://instagram.com/funselektor
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/artofrally

The new racing game from the creator of Absolute Drift! 

Race in the golden era of rally. Drive 50+ iconic cars from the 60s to 90s on challenging stages through stylized environments like Finland, Norway and Japan. Will you master the art of rally?

Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/user/Nassault630
Music: https://tatreal.pro/
